data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Welcome to the exclusive Bell Tower Community where luxury meets sophistication. This exquisite home boasts quality craftsmanship, character, and timeless design. Step inside and be greeted by the custom office, great room, and family room cabinetry that exudes warmth and elegance. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line appliances including a Subzero fridge, Miele dishwasher, and a Wolf oven/range. No expenses were spared in creating this culinary masterpiece. Offering an array of custom features such as solid wood 8-foot doors, iron cast railings, and a workout room, this home is truly exceptional. Retreat to the private covered patio and yard, perfect for indoor-outdoor living. With over $200,000 in recent upgrades, this home is in immaculate and pristine condition. Don't miss your opportunity to own this luxurious haven. Assumable VA loan with a $310,000 balance at 2.25% interest.
